          }
        },
        {
          "level": 3,
          "type": "heading",
          "text": "Configuring the Screen Mode of an External Display",
          "anchor": "1653243"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Many screens support multiple resolutions, some of which use different pixel aspect ratios. Screen objects use the most common screen mode by default, but you can change that mode to one that is more suitable for your content. For example, if you are implementing a game using OpenGL ES and your textures are designed for a 640 x 480 pixel screen, you might change the screen mode for screens with higher default resolutions."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If you plan to use a screen mode other than the default one, apply that mode to the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uiscreen"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " object before associating the screen with a window. The "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uiscreenmode"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " class defines the attributes of a single screen mode. You can get a list of the modes supported by a screen from its "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uiscreen/1617839-availablemodes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property and iterate through the list for one that matches your needs."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "For more information about screen modes, see "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uiscreenmode"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
